# Telegram Task Manager Bot

Telegram-бот для управления задачами с AI-парсингом текста и голоса.

## Stack

- Runtime: Node.js + TypeScript (tsx)
- Bot framework: grammY + @grammyjs/conversations
- ORM: Prisma + PostgreSQL
- AI: Groq SDK (Llama 3.1 8B for text parsing, Whisper Large v3 Turbo for STT)
- Scheduler: node-cron
- Linter/Formatter: Biome
- Git hooks: Husky v9 + lint-staged

## Architecture

- Modular structure: each feature is a grammY `Composer` in `src/modules/`
- Prisma Client singleton in `src/db/client.ts`
- AI services in `src/services/` (ai.ts for LLM, stt.ts for speech-to-text)
- Shared types exported from `src/types/index.ts`
- Config via environment variables loaded in `src/config.ts`

## Key directories

```
src/
├── index.ts          — entry point
├── bot.ts            — bot setup, middleware chain
├── config.ts         — env vars, constants
├── db/client.ts      — Prisma client singleton
├── modules/          — feature modules (tasks, projects, voice, reminders)
├── services/         — AI services (ai.ts, stt.ts)
└── types/            — shared TypeScript types
```

## Commands

- `pnpm dev` — run in watch mode
- `pnpm start` — run once
- `pnpm build` — TypeScript compilation
- `pnpm lint` — Biome check
- `pnpm db:migrate` — Prisma migrations
- `pnpm db:generate` — generate Prisma client
